<div>

  <div class="header">
    <p class="date">{{momentDateFormat currentDate "DD MMM YYYY"}}<span class="T1" /></p>

    <p class="address">
      {{recipient.firstName}}
      {{recipient.initials}}
      {{recipient.lastName}}
      <br />
      {{recipient.address}}
      <br />
      {{recipient.city}},
      {{recipient.province}}
      <br />
      {{recipient.country}},
      {{recipient.postalCode}}
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="saluation">
    Dear
    {{recipient.firstName}}:
  </p>

  <div class="body">
    <p>I am pleased to inform you that your Yukon Grant application to attend full-time
      post-secondary has been approved as follows:</p>

    <div>
      <p class="flex justify-between">
        <strong>Program: {{program.name}}</strong>
        <span>
          <strong>Start Date:</strong>
          <span class="ml-4">{{momentDateFormat program.startDate "MMM Do YYYY"}}</span>
        </span>
      </p>
      <p class="flex justify-between">
        <strong>Institution: {{ program.institutionName }}</strong>
        <span>
          <strong>End Date:</strong>
          <span class="ml-4">{{momentDateFormat program.endDate "MMM Do YYYY"}}</span>
        </span>
      </p>

      <p class="P2">
        <strong>Rate per Week:</strong>
        <span class="ml-8">{{centsToDollarString program.ratePerWeekInCents }}</span>
      </p>

      <p class="P2"><strong>Approv. Weeks:</strong><span class="T3">        </span><span class="T4">xx</span></p>

      <p><strong>Travel/Airfare:</strong><span class="T3">               
        </span><span class="T4">$xxxx.xx</span></p>
    </div>
    <p class="P3">Disbursements<span> Issue Date – Based on confirmed enrollment before each
        semester</span>

    </p>
    <p class="P2"><span class="T4">$xxxx.xx</span><span class="T3">                </span><span class="T4">Mmm
        yyyy</span>
    </p>

    <p><span class="T4">$xxxx.xx</span><span class="T3">                </span><span class="T4">Mmm
        yyyy</span>
    </p>
    <p class="P5"> </p>
    <p><span class="T3">If any of the above information is incorrect or you withdraw from full-time
        studies or drop to part-time status, you may have to repay some or all of your Yukon Grant.</span></p>

    <p><span class="T3">Your first disbursement has been processed. </span><strong>If more than one
        payment is listed above, you will be required to submit a Program Information Form (PIF)
        confirming full-time status prior to the release of any subsequent disbursements.</strong><span class="T3">
        Our office will accept PIFs completed by the institution and submitted directly to
      </span><a href="mailto:sfa@yukon.ca" class="Internet_20_link"><span class="Internet_20_link"><span
            class="T3">sfa@yukon.ca</span></span></a><span class="T3">
        as early as one month before the issue date(s) outlined above. You can download the PIF at
        http://yukon.ca/en/program-information-student-financial-assistance.</span></p>

    <p class="P4">If you have any questions regarding your assessment, please contact our office by
      email at sfa@yukon.ca, by telephone at 867-667-5929, or toll free within Yukon at
      1-800-661-0408 ext. 5929.
      <span class="T3" />
    </p>

    <p><span class="T3">Congratulations on your decision to further your education. On behalf of the
        Department of Education, I wish you the very best in your studies.  </span></p>
  </div>

  <p class="P4">Sincerely,<span class="T3" /></p>
  <p class="P6"> </p>
  <p class="P8"><span class="T2">SFAOFirst SFAOLast</span><span class="T1"><br />Student Financial
      Services Officer<br />Student Funding Programs
    </span></p>
</div>
